name: Aubjex Development Kit
short_description: The Aubjex Development Kit is a multifaceted collection of frameworks that augment the Java SE JDK. Provides a different model for GUI, distributed systems, io, threads and data collections. Does not use swing or rmi. Depends on a small subset of JDK 6.
